message:
[ROCKETMQ-291] Fix System.out.printf throws UnknownFormatConversionException

Author: lindzh <linsony0@163.com>

Closes #168 from lindzh/fix_print.

added: System.out.printf("The sub command %s not exist.%n", args[1]);
